Everyone,

Can harmony and resonance be had? Yes it can. It takes a certain level of acceptance though. You have to accept the fact that every entity in existence is not spiritually equal but has the capability to become equal. Every entity has a right to this knowledge and has the ability to gain it with or without technical means. You have to accept that all realities are true in the eyes of those who behold them. Finally, you have to respect and accept people for what they are and know that all things will work out exactly how they are supposed to.

Regards,
Frank R.

